Package: segMINT
Type: Package
Title: Process MINT Simulation Results and Create DuckDB Databases
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Cosmo", "Santoni", , "cosmo.santoni@imperial.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to process MINT simulation results stored in RDS files,
    flatten nested parameters, and create DuckDB databases for efficient querying.
    Includes functions to handle batch processing of simulation files and manage
    problematic simulations.
